工作內容:
The Industry Liason Officer role is to build and develop the mutual interest and benefits with industry by aligned with the strategic program and pratices based on the mission of the Foundation. 
•	Share the value and mission for the Foundation. 
•	Responsible for developing and engaging the strategic relationship and alliance with the industry especially focus on Servcies, Tourism and Education industry;  
•	Work out the success plan and practices to develop long- and short-term launch program that support the mutual benefits with industry and the Foundation; 
•	Act the communication representative of the Foundation to cover the engagement and connections with local and oversea stakeholders, including but not limit to institutes, non-profit organization, partner, school and enterprises and so on whenever needed;  
•	Be able to own and work out the program and project details on daily basis and end-to-end deliverables independently.
•	Ad-hoc project and assignments appointed by CEO, Foundation and the Group.
